{"tid":1803323,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"當年既民革好似現在既黃色經濟圈！！！！","createTime":"2019-12-30T06:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T06:36:16.000Z","uid":241151,"like":2,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"9840e66c771e8777a9371a37f051e58a7532a3f3","tid":1803323,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:24:38.000Z","msg":"需要靠有錢佬支持同共產黨俾機會既各大主流傳媒，又咁橋同建制陣營一黑一白唱雙黃，去谷黃色經濟圈，手法同之前忽然吹人去守大學，背棄流水抗爭，送人去死既狀況好似<br />\n<br />\n共產黨控制了傳媒及網媒，果然是最佳招式，想點帶風向點玩都得"},{"pid":"f318959c145cde2f7fb5e3bdf99d1882600171a1","tid":1803323,"uid":198590,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:24:57.000Z","msg":"會員 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">#241151 - 瀧野由美仔</span></strong> 極有可能係<span style=\"color: gold;\">五毛, 分化撚, mon-post狗或網軍</span><br />\n請大家保持批判性思考，善用不推文回覆，該會員以往言論：<br />\n<br />\n<code>人地學生就打生打死，鄺神都好自得其樂 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YW4Wctv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYW4Wctv.jpg&h=1310c14d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n唉&hellip;&hellip;唔好問我點解香港抗爭咁多年都係咁失敗，香港人情況仲越來越差<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fhaha.gif&h=20aa0304&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fno.gif&h=29da48de&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1714163/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺... - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>想知乜嘢叫流水式...集會?<br />\n流水就不可能集合，集合可能是在新屋嶺...<br />\n會唔會太過 creative, creative 到亂Q咁嚟。<br />\n定你哋較為喜愛嗌D無意思的口號，做無意義的事，好似時代革命，摺紙咁。</blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696584/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>改口號啦！[香港人！送頭！] - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>香港人！送頭！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1696549/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>點呀？之前係咪話過要追究返邊d人，邊d網，邊d團體同傳媒吹市去送頭既？ - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/T2b0VZQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FT2b0VZQ.jpg&h=2ac5df0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n原來係連登x蘋果吹雞<br />\n難怪有哂地點時間表<br />\n鑊鑊都港島，鑊鑊都推人去死<br />\n流人哋嘅血成就自己得票當選！<br />\n泛民蘋果全部都要仆街冚家鏟！<br />\n<br />\n好彩我一早就同班泛民左膠割晒蓆姐，分化實在好！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fsmile.gif&h=0b593ebc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n快d回&quot;拉，不分化，不推文回覆啦&quot;<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fdog%2Fzzz.gif&h=b6af20bd&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1691882/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>香港既和理非從來唔保護勇武，甚至會阻止勇武制服勇武出賣勇武，所以和理非實則係港奸 - #1</code><br />\n<blockquote>泛民港奸！<img src=\"http://www.lihkg.com/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.lihkg.com%2Fassets%2Ffaces%2Fnormal%2Fagree.gif&h=7a38d91f&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><a href=\"http://lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lihkg.com/thread/1661812/page/1?ref=sharer&amp;post=1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n意見及舉報： <a href=\"http://lih.kg/1707551\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">lih.kg/1707551</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/965Ev7E.jpg\" />"},{"pid":"d7527d47045aa7927636dc41e39bf99e68fa23d2","tid":1803323,"uid":241151,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:26:20.000Z","msg":"唔駛拗喇咁多位暗共泛民左膠，橫掂你地都冇貨，我係五毛我係阿sir，夠未？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e569e38bc8616298d225b43d88396eee928c94e4","tid":1803323,"uid":55973,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:26:25.000Z","msg":"又一隻"},{"pid":"723f3f8d579447f2f1e70509fc27daa60af5edb1","tid":1803323,"uid":305536,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:26:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>德國聯署有三份  呢家仲有一份未達標 <span style=\"color: red;\">最後兩日</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1802070\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1802070</a><br />\n<br />\n德國減少對中國和其他非民主國家的依賴<br />\n<a href=\"https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fepetitionen.bundestag.de%2Fpetitionen%2F_2019%2F_09%2F_01%2FPetition_98731.html&d=LK0Ahc5Iz%2F4EhQQuEN3KkVYPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=c899abc4\" target=\"_blank\">https://epetitionen.bundestag.de/petitionen/_2019/_09/_01/Petition_98731.html</a></blockquote>"},{"pid":"923f01684e81660b1277b4e2a4a217cc525318c0","tid":1803323,"uid":2772,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-30T06:27:41.000Z","msg":"香港人 講現在<br />\n哈"},{"pid":"5c109097f55ed6a8f0d64806d466dc227760fc03","tid":1803323,"uid":177150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019